element.name: Hermit 5 - Jailhouse Rock!! by MaryAnn42, Traditional Cache (1.5/1.5)
element.description:
Important: Bring your own pen. Please re-hide carefully. Park Opening Times
Nov – Jan 9.00 – 16.30 Feb 9.00 – 17.00 Mar 9.00 – 18.00 Apr 9.00 – 20.00 May - Aug 9.00 – 21.00 Sept 9.00 – 20.00 Oct 9.00 – 18.00
element.long-description: Beside the river is a small watchtower/jailhouse folly. There are steps up to the higher open grounds above. This scenic walk is very popular with adults and children alike.

ul.li:
2010-06-08T19:00:00Z : Found it by polorein
What a miserable day cache found very well camouflaged nicely hidden.

2010-05-15T19:00:00Z : Found it by Timmolly
Our first find! A few mugglers around but we were discreet [8D]

2010-05-07T19:00:00Z : Found it by milottie
Very nice hide.. was just the ticket for the trip to the park today. TFTC. SL

2010-04-05T19:00:00Z : Found it by didi2206
Great park, great cache!!! Thanks

2010-04-03T19:00:00Z : Found it by ButcherBoys
Went on to this one after eggstravaganza, lovely walk, despite peeing it down. Had to run for car, wring out and head for home!!!!! TFTC

2010-02-13T20:00:00Z : Found it by Kersti.com
After finding the Cave so quickly we thought this would be simple. Took us a bit longer to get there than planned as we stopped at the museum, which was pretty good and well worth a visit. Finally headed round to this one and had the cache in hand in record time. Thanks for bringing us to this wonderful park.
